cdata.name: Asia Coin
cdata.desc: Asia Coin is a Scrypt Coin with a very brief PoW phase of two weeks or 20,000 blocks. The PoW phase is scheduled to produce 40% of the hard capped limit of 360 million. The PoS phase is set for ten years with first year stake interest set at a high 100% - whcih subsequently drops to 2%. Block time is 60 seconds, difficulty retargets every block and there was no premine.
